title: [Gorget Trails, East Cliff Face]
description: A slight misstep from this rocky prominence would mean a long and painful fall.  The air has a chilly bite to it, despite the clear, bright sunshine.  A papery ribbon of discarded snakeskin flutters in the wind, snagged under a speckled blue rock.

A slight misstep from this rocky prominence would mean a long and painful fall.  The night air is extremely cold, now that the sun has gone into hiding.  A papery ribbon of discarded snakeskin flutters in the wind, snagged under a speckled blue rock.
